lines.text: You could have been arrested and gone to jail for five years!
Then why don't you call the police and put us all out of our misery?
If you ever drink and drive again, I will.
How many different ways do I have to tell you to leave me alone?
Just give me your car keys. I mean you shouldn't have driven here in the first place. You can go to jail for that.
Why don't you turn me in? You're good at that!
Give me your keys. I am not gonna let another friend die.
I am not your friend. Remember?
I don't care! You have to give me your keys.
I just want away from you!
